WEBVTT

00:00.000 --> 00:18.000
If your first prompt is usually a messy draft, RyFine is the fastest way to turn it into something an AI model can actually execute well.

00:18.000 --> 00:44.000
RyFine is local-first. You choose the provider and model, your keys stay in this browser, and Browser AI or Ollama can run without a hosted API at all.

00:44.000 --> 01:45.000
Paste your raw prompt into the left pane. Add a hosted key once if you need it, then hit RyFine and watch the refined prompt stream into the output pane.

01:45.000 --> 02:18.000
This works best when you know the task but not the cleanest way to ask for it. RyFine keeps your intent and removes ambiguity before you spend tokens downstream.

02:18.000 --> 02:30.000
Try RyFine now and sharpen your next prompt in one pass.